    {
      "assets": [],
      "author": "fancive",
      "description": "## Bug Fixes\n- Replace unsafe type casts with `instanceof` guards\n- Eliminate unsafe `as unknown as` casts in scroll.ts\n- Add logging to silent catch blocks\n- Close abort signal race window in streaming fetch\n- Make `normalizeSettings` return new object instead of mutating input\n- Prevent modal confirmation promise from resolving twice\n- Add error handling to fire-and-forget async patterns\n- Remove unsafe fallback cast in `CardEditModal` constructor\n- Pass `--max-tokens` to Claude Code CLI to prevent output truncation\n- Salvage truncated LLM JSON and make errors copyable\n\n## Refactoring\n- Extract body builders and types to `provider-bodies.ts`\n- Extract card rendering and context menu from `view.ts render()`\n- Extract batch folder prompt dialog to `batch.ts`\n- Extract `resolveCardAnchors` and `confirmRegenerateEditedCards` from `main.ts`\n- Extract `runForFile` error handler and streaming callback\n- Replace magic numbers in `scroll.ts` with named constants\n\n## Testing\n- Add comprehensive test coverage across multiple modules\n- Edge case tests for cache, streaming, batch, providers, schema, i18n, vault\n\n## Code Quality\n- Upgrade biome `noNonNullAssertion` and `noImplicitAnyLet` to error\n- Fix import ordering and formatting per biome rules",
      "draft": false,
      "name": "1.0.5",
      "prerelease": false,
      "publishedAt": "2026-04-27T06:45:11Z",
      "tag": "1.0.5"
    },
